{"title":"白石老人的诗","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":1,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"白石老人的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花开天下正风雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷杀长安市上人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑倒牡丹无福命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开时虽暖已残春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双松立雪图"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁暮寒风烈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长松立冰雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人知心后凋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见通身节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松小时或砍其枝，必留数寸，以保松之不死，树长大，所留枝包在树内，皮外不得见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独脚凳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吾乡牧童坐者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独脚一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散手倒卧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁为扶持"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自家稳坐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"题友人冷庵画卷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对君斯册感当年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撞破金瓯国可怜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镫下再三挥泪看"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华无此整山川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"樊山老人后人学画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采桑图乞题句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桑干叶少得归迟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人并蚕饥有所思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪把鸳鸯绣衣者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那知五月卖新丝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往事示儿辈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村书无角宿缘迟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"廿七年华始有师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镫盏无油何害事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自烧松火读唐书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"余少苦贫，二十七岁始得胡沁园、陈少蕃二师，王仲言社弟兼师也。朝为木工，夜则以松火读书。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}